ge such demoniac men are striving to reach the higher planetary systems by mechanical arrangement. These are examples of bewilderment. The result is that, without their knowledge, they are gliding \ntoward hell. Here the Sanskrit word mohaj\xe2\x88\x92la is very significant. J\xe2\x88\x92la means net; like fishes caught in a net, they have no way to come out.
